sub_title: Management Consulting Manager - Talent & Organization practice at Accenture
summary: Helping customers with complex transformations and developing new approaches is what drives me every day. I enjoy working in- and with teams where I aim to establish an inspiring atmosphere that promotes communication and collaboration. My previous studies in globalization culture and work experience in Paris and Barcelona additionally provide me with a high level of cultural awareness and an international mindset. In my free time I like cooking, fine dining and traveling to exotic destinations.
